item.description: I am a visiting student at UC Merced, supervised by Prof. Ming-Hsuan Yang. My research interests include computer vision and deep learning. After taking several Computer Science and Machine Learning courses at UC Berkeley and NTU, along with my past research experiences as a research assistant at VSLab, NTHU and an intern at an AI startup, RelaJet, I decided to switch field from Finance to Computer Science. I would like to pursue a Ph.
